summary:
I provide people with tools to release stress and let go of unwanted, limiting beliefs.

Those tools can be used 'on the spot', no matter what situation you are in.

It's my passion to share with you the knowledge and the know how that have helped me and my clients change, be happier, healthier and wealthier.

We have no idea how stuck we were until the stuckness is dissolved and until we experience our freedom.

We all WANT to change some of our old patterns and behaviors don't we.......
And most of us have to come to the conclusion that after a while our willpower just was NOT enough to stick to our plans.

Recognize that?

Let me help you discover why and how to resolve resistance to change : that is my greatest joy right now!

I have made a very usefull and unique combination of different kind of techniques, protocols, tools and programs so that you can really make change happen.

And yes, it takes some effort but let me tell you this : JUST IN THE BEGINNING!

Once you have implemented some new behaviors in your life, you will notice how things will change for the better! Look for the evidence in your life and even the tiniest proof will give you the motivation and inspiration to go on with this program and continue to MOVE ON and create the life you want.

This particular program can be offered in Dutch or in English
